%% INTERNET EDGE
Internet((Internet))
Internet --> ISP[ISP Router<br>192.168.101.1]

ISP --> FW[Edge Firewall<br>router-fw<br>NAT / VPN / Port Forward<br>192.168.101.185<br>10.0.0.1]

FW --> CoreR[Core Router<br>L3 Routing<br>10.0.99.3]

%% CORE NETWORK SPLIT
CoreR --> MgmtSW[MGMT Switch<br>10.0.99.0/24]
CoreR --> LANSW[LAN Switch<br>10.0.10.0/24]
CoreR --> DMZSW[DMZ Switch<br>10.0.20.0/24]

%% MGMT NETWORK
subgraph MGMT_VMs["MGMT VM Layer (Proxmox VMs)"]
